* Panitz-Cohen, Nava; Mullins, Robert A. and Bonfil, Ruhama 2016. Second Preliminary Report of the Excavations at Tell Abil el Qameḥ (Abel Beth Maacah). &quot;Strata&quot; 33: 35–59.
* Panitz-Cohen, Nava; Yahalom-Mack, Naama 2022. Tel Avel Bet Ma‘akha (Abel Beth Maacah) – 2018–2021. Hadashot Archaeologiot Journal, vol. 134. 
* Schneidewind, William M. 1996. Tel Dan Stela – New Light on Aramaic and Jehu&#x27;s Revolt. &quot;Bulletin of the American Schools of Oriental Research&quot; 302: 75–90.
* Stepansky, Yosef, (2005). Tel Avel Bet Ma&#x27;akha. Hadashot Archaeologiot Journal, vol. 117. IAA report on 2000 discovery of Middle Bronze II burial remains at southeastern foot of the lower mound.
